#InvoiceActivationDoneText:
In order for you to accept online payments, we need to perform a quick review of the types of products you’re selling. Keep an eye on your email and we’ll let you know when we’re done.

If you’ve already received the email, then you’re ready to send your first invoice. All you do is add items to your cart, choose “Invoice” during checkout and enter your details. We’ll send your invoice right away.
